Body:
collection = lookup.TemplateLookup()
collection.put_string('base.html',
    """
            <%def name="foo()">
                base.foo
            </%def>

            <%def name="bat()">
                base.bat
            </%def>
"""
    )
collection.put_string('lib.html',
    """
            <%inherit file="base.html"/>
            <%def name="bar()">
                lib.bar
                ${parent.foo()}
                ${self.foo()}
                ${parent.bat()}
                ${self.bat()}
            </%def>

            <%def name="foo()">
                lib.foo
            </%def>

        """
    )
collection.put_string('front.html',
    """
            <%namespace name="lib" file="lib.html"/>
            ${lib.bar()}
        """
    )
assert result_lines(collection.get_template('front.html').render()) == [
    'lib.bar', 'base.foo', 'lib.foo', 'base.bat', 'base.bat']
